#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.22:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Saraṇānivagga "
msgstr "3. About Sarakāni "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Dutiyamahānāmasutta "
msgstr "22. With Mahānāma (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.22:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn55.22:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, near Kapilavatthu in the Banyan Tree Monastery. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho mahānāmo sakko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Mahānāma the Sakyan went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.22:1.4"
msgid "“idaṃ, bhante, kapilavatthu iddhañceva phītañca bāhujaññaṃ ākiṇṇamanussaṃ sambādhabyūhaṃ. "
msgstr "“Sir, this Kapilavatthu is successful and prosperous and full of people, with cramped cul-de-sacs. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.5"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ vā payirupāsitvā manobhāvanīye vā bhikkhū sāyanhasamayaṃ kapilavatthuṃ pavisanto; "
msgstr "In the late afternoon, after paying homage to the Buddha or an esteemed mendicant, I enter Kapilavatthu. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.6"
msgid "bhantenapi hatthinā samāgacchāmi; "
msgstr "I encounter a stray elephant, "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.7"
msgid "bhantenapi assena samāgacchāmi; "
msgstr "horse, "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.8"
msgid "bhantenapi rathena samāgacchāmi; "
msgstr "chariot, "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.9"
msgid "bhantenapi sakaṭena samāgacchāmi; "
msgstr "cart, "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.10"
msgid "bhantenapi purisena samāgacchāmi. "
msgstr "or person. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.11"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, tasmiṃ samaye mussateva bhagavantaṃ ārabbha sati, mussati dhammaṃ ārabbha sati, mussati saṅghaṃ ārabbha sati. "
msgstr "At that time I lose mindfulness regarding the Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.12"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "I think: "

msgctxt "sn55.22:1.13"
msgid "‘imamhi cāhaṃ samaye kālaṃ kareyyaṃ, kā mayhaṃ gati, ko abhisamparāyo’”ti? "
msgstr "‘If I were to die at this time, where would I be reborn in my next life?’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.22:2.1"
msgid "“Mā bhāyi, mahānāma, mā bhāyi, mahānāma. "
msgstr "“Do not fear, Mahānāma, do not fear! "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.2"
msgid "Apāpakaṃ te maraṇaṃ bhavissati apāpikā kālaṅkiriyā. "
msgstr "Your death will not be a bad one; your passing will not be a bad one. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.3"
msgid "Catūhi kho, mahānāma, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has four things slants, slopes, and inclines towards extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.4"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.5"
msgid "Idha, mahānāma, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.6"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.7"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.8"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.22:2.9"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn55.22:3.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, mahānāma, rukkho pācīnaninno pācīnapoṇo pācīnapabbhāro, so mūlacchinno katamena papateyyā”ti? "
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that slants, slopes, and inclines to the east. If it was cut off at the root where would it fall?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.22:3.2"
msgid "“Yena, bhante, ninno yena poṇo yena pabbhāro”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, it would fall in the direction that it slants, slopes, and inclines.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.22:3.3"
msgid "“Evameva kho, mahānāma, imehi catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti. "
msgstr "“In the same way, a noble disciple who has four things slants, slopes, and inclines towards extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.22:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

